<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>AirWX</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body{font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; margin:24px;}
        .card{border:1px solid #ddd; padding:16px; border-radius:12px; max-width:620px;}
        .btn{display:inline-block; padding:10px 14px; border:1px solid #222; border-radius:8px;
             background:#fff; text-decoration:none; cursor:pointer; margin-right:8px;}
        .hint{color:#666; font-size:14px;}
        hr{border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee; margin:18px 0;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>AirWX</h1>

<div class="card">
    <h3>날씨</h3>
    <p>시계열 적재 수: <b>{{wxCount}}</b></p>
    <form method="post" action="/ingest/weather" style="margin-top:12px">
        <button class="btn" type="submit">수동 적재 (POST)</button>
    </form>
    <p style="margin-top:10px">
        <a class="btn" href="/ingest/weather">GET 실행 (실데이터)</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/ingest/weather?mock=1">GET 실행 (목데이터)</a>
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h3>대기질</h3>
    <p>시계열 적재 수: <b>{{aqCount}}</b></p>
    <form method="post" action="/ingest/air" style="margin-top:12px">
        <button class="btn" type="submit">수동 적재 (POST)</button>
    </form>
    <p style="margin-top:10px">
        <a class="btn" href="/ingest/air">GET 실행 (실데이터)</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/ingest/air?mock=1">GET 실행 (목데이터)</a>
    </p>

    <p class="hint">스케줄러 켜두면 주기적으로 적재되게 확장할 수 있어요.</p>
</div>

<p style="margin-top:16px">
    <a class="btn" href="/h2">H2 Console</a>
    <span class="hint">— JDBC: <code>jdbc:h2:file:./.h2/airwx</code> / user: <code>sa</code></span>
</p>
</body>
</html>
